metadata.name: Cold Key
metadata.description: Thank you for being apart of this incredible mission of ours creating art & supporting independent Musicians alike. This is your Key Pass to unlock Project Blue, a decentralized web3 music label backing independent artists, Twitter in bio for more details. Your Cold Key is one of the 20 produced beats & acts as a pass to an up coming rap album featuring Caskey & other artists SIIILV3R has collaborated with in the last 3 years of starting this vision. Project Blue's Mission is to create music independently while helping others find their dreams through consistent hard work and motivation. The world is ours to experience and this is only the beginning for key holders. Utility including private networking & future hold to earn can be found on the Official Twitter Page @ProjectBlue_NFT
